From: Jakub Kicinski <kuba@kernel.org>
Date: Fri, 1 Oct 2021 14:32:27 -0700
Subject: fddi: use eth_hw_addr_set()
Patch-mainline: v5.16-rc1
Git-commit: 4d3d2c8dba360e5f8a9bf9d4b4f7d829e9812593
